/*********************************************************************/
/*STD    CLPBASEBND                                                  */
/*EXI    TEXT('Midas SM Change reporting code fields')               */
/*********************************************************************/
/*                                                                   */
/*       Midas - Implementation Module                               */
/*                                                                   */
/*       SMC000018 - Migrate Reporting Code Fields                   */
